answer: I'd probably add that Application.ProcessMessages here probably is more a band-aid than a solution. There's always a chance that the chain of messages triggered by GetInvItemRecord don't come back in time to get processed by that first call, and you'll need to put another call, and then another... It's probably better to use some sort of "OnDataReceived" event on the Record class, which hopefully exists.
